                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>AURORA is a premium health and lifestyle smart ring designed to track your body 24/7 — sleep, heart rate, SpO2, activity, and more — all from an elegant wide-band ring with a glossy black ceramic finish and a built-in LED display. No subscription required.</p>",
